{"tid":2363166,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬來西亞進入緊急狀態，以遏止新型肺炎疫情","createTime":"2021-01-12T04:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T04:37:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62e5bd9908e3227351a47b203f31a9b0f0f3e9a3","tid":2363166,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:25:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569935-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569935-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuTw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=3915a829\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569935-20210112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4660f1bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569935-20210112.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞國家元首阿卜杜拉宣布，全國進入緊急狀態至8月1日，以遏止新型肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n皇宮表示，阿布杜拉認為新型冠狀病毒正在國內擴散，目前處於關鍵階段，有必要宣布緊急狀態。在緊急狀態下，總理及內閣獲賦予特別權力，容許政府未經國會批准製定法律。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞上星期單日破紀錄新增3000宗確診病例，全國累計13萬8000宗確診，555名患者死亡。總理毛希丁昨日宣布全國旅遊禁令，首都吉隆坡與5個州實施14天封鎖，指大馬的醫療體系瀕臨崩潰。"},{"pid":"5e3a3b4221304817b3113ff759befd5f17ed4206","tid":2363166,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:26:07.000Z","msg":"有共產黨一日<br />\n中國病毒係唔會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad32400eee40b8e1ecd67d77722f01f06be60e95","tid":2363166,"uid":217641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"至8月1日??"},{"pid":"1911767a19ea3876ce41a419b787b91f94d21946","tid":2363166,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad32400eee40b8e1ecd67d77722f01f06be60e95","tid":2363166,"uid":217641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"至8月1日??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"即係封八個月<img src=\"/assets/f